# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# comment.py  —  AI LinkedIn commenting for profile warmth & visibility
#
# Strategy: find posts by ICP-matching people, generate genuine comments,
# let user approve, then post via Playwright. Max 5 comments/day.
#
# Safety by design:
#   - Max 5 comments/day (far below LinkedIn's limits)
#   - 3+ minute gaps between comments
#   - User must approve every comment before it's posted
#   - Genuine, non-salesy comments generated by Claude
#   - Session cookies refreshed and saved after every browser run
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
